GRID is majorly used in case of 2D structures
1. grid-template-columns->used for specifying column ratio or size
2. grid-template-rows->used for specifying row ratio or size

sample code 

 .container{
      display: grid;
      gap:0px;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      height: 800px;
      width: 800px;
      
    }
    .white{
      background-color:#f0d9b5 ;
     
    }
    .black{
      background-color:#b58863 ;
     
    }
